CallbackIntefaces Callback interface.
CommandAbstract<C,U extends CallbackIntefaces.OnCallback> Command is the abstract classs for the command.
CommandManager CommandManager manages Commands in CommandCollection.
GenericListener  
MultimediaController MultimediaController will be the template class for the thre MultimediaAbstract objects, Picture, SoundClip and Video.
MultimediaControllerManager MultimediaControllerManager merges all 3 controller into one to abstract developer from choosing which.
OnActivityResultListener OnActivityResultListener is a listener for when returning result from an activity.
OnAddMultimediaListener OnAddMultimediaCommand is the command for handling adding Multimedias.
OnDeleteMultimediaListener OnDeleteMultimediaListener is the command for handling deleting Multimedias.
OnExitListener exitActivityCommand contains the call back for exiting current activity.
OnMoveMultimediaListener ONMoveMultimediaListener is the command for handling moving Multimedias.
OnRedoListener XXX DO NOT ADD THIS TO THE CommandManager stack.
OnSaveListener Command for saving.
OnStartPageEditListener Listener when starting PageEdit view.
OnSwipeTouchListener  
OnUndoListener XXX DO NOT ADD THIS TO THE CommandManager stack.
PageAdapter PageAdapter utilizes the Adapter Pattern as discussed in class.
PictureController PictureController helps abstract the loadBitmap method as this is system dependent therefore not suitable in the model package.
SoundClipController SoundClipController helps abstract the loadBitmap, Play, Pause and Stop method as this is system dependent therefore not suitable in the model package.
VideoController VideoController is part of the MVC pattern that act as a bridge between model and the view.
